sources.description:
**This film is under license from Vision Films Inc.  All rights reserved**

Out of the Darkness - Eli is a man in his twenties with a calling on his life from a young age, but he's been running from that calling - a modern day Jonah. After being fired by his father, arguing with his girlfriend in front of their daughter, and then a visit to the local pub, Eli decides to get out of town. On a lonely mountain highway Eli misses a turn and careens over an embankment, landing deep in the forest.

Stars  - John Lewis, Graham Greene, Sherry Morris
